name: FASTPORT PASSPORT
tag_list: passport, passports, fast-passport, expedited-passport, get-passport, new-passport, emergency-passport, passport-renewal
overview: Fastportpassport.com is a private company and is registered with the US Passport Agencies in New York, Boston, and Philadelphia. We specialize in expediting your passport and visa applications as quickly as 24 hours Nationwide. We are not a government agency or the passport office. Our business is to provide your travel documents quickly, easily, and stress-free, but customers are able to apply for passport services directly by visiting the US Government link below. As a registered passport expeditor we charge a service fee (on top) of the government fee to secure your passport in the time you requested starting as low as $79. Government fees are not included in our service plans if you choose to use the government you will only pay applicable fees. Government service (costs less) then using Fastportpassport.com
